latestIgtvVideos.caption:
STYLING FAUX LEATHER SKIRT IN 8 DIFFERENT WAYS
Today’s topic is leather skirt, which is must have of any season. Designers and celebrities gave us green light to rock the show in leather skirts everywhere we want. They try to add this garment in every new collection, offering different kind of shades and hues, including blue, red, burgundy, white, green and of course black.
The best thing about leather skirts is that they can be styled in million ways. All depends on its design, color, cut and of course your own taste. These skirts are meant not only for sporty girls and edgy biker chics. That’s why leather skirts can be worn at the office, as they look smart and sophisticated at the same time. What I find amazing in leather skirts is the appearance of each style. It can be dressed with any outfit you have in your wardrobe, like an old t-shirts or granny’s sweater.
Some TIPS:

1) If you like showing off your pretty legs, wear mini leather skirts, like tight or pleated A-line or super large. It will look amazing with denim shirts, jumpers, pullovers, cozy coats etc.

2) If you are going out, try on hot heels or flat boots. Or go for a laid back style wear converse and ballet pumps.

3)For a more sophisticated look I would wear slim leather skirts with knitted tops and ankle boots. I personally like how leather skirts look with jumpers, parkas and flat boots.

4) Leather skirts go perfect as: office look, dinner out look, party look, cocktail party look, date out look and many more.
5) This garment can be worn all year round, just add tights in the winter time and sandals in the summer.

6)There are cool pencil over-the-knee styles which look stunning with heels, casual top, blazer, jewelry and fabulous handbag.

Thanks me later 💜💜
My fav look is with the cropped Blazer which one is yours ????

#fauxleather #leatherskirt #leatherblazer #trends2022 #stylingvideo #lookbook

“10 DIFFERENT WAYS TO STYLE AN BLACK OVERSIZED BLAZER”

Oversized Blazer looks are very much the thing right now! An Oversized Blazer is an essential piece that goes with everything and gives every look a trendy finishing touch. Thinking about that, I wanted to show you, how to style oversized blazer @zara in 10 different ways!!!

I cannot go without a blazer look neither in winter nor in summer times. The unbeatable advantage of the Oversized Blazer version is, that even though it has the chiseled shoulder points and small waistline as other formal jackets do, it has a looser fit and therefore creates a more relaxed silhouette.

The Oversized Blazer comes in a broad variety of different lengths, volumes, materials and colors!! 

Speaking of winter/fall looks – what about an Oversized Blazer worn over a maxi dress or long skirt? Yehhh those are my fav look!!
Do let me know your fav 🌸🌸🌸
.

latestPosts.caption:
Do I miss shooting!!! Yeh hell Yes!!!!! 
 Healing is a process and I am embracing the process calmly and patiently !!! Will be back next month !!!! Till enjoy once in a blue post 🥰
Just to remind you all !! I exist 😜

Outfit deets 
Top @savana @savanaonyou 
Trousers @zara 
Bag @miraggiolife 
Shades @hm

Just a random post coz bored of bed rest and can’t shoot as I haven’t recovered yet !!! Lately life is all about my room and my bed, medicines , supplements , braces and crutches !! Missing shooting, going out, my gym, my dance class !!!! 
This is the first time in my life that I feel so stuck but Yehhh!!! I think I needed this break to reflect on my life !!! One thing I realise that Health is everything if your health is not good then no amount of money can give you happiness!!! 
Also in time like these you get to know who your real friends are and who are not !!!! Though I am lucky enough to have people around me who are taking care of me and treating me like princess !! So full of gratitude and feeling blessed !!! 
Can’t wait to get back on my both feet 🙈 and start creating content 😎
Neer Jaisingh
